  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The proposed front lightwell and associated works would, by reason of design, scale and location, would appear as an unsympathetic and discordant addition to both the host building and wider streetscene, resulting in an adverse impact to character and appearance of the host building and wider area. As such the proposed development is contrary D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach), and D4 (Delivering good design) of the London Plan (2021), policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 (2020), and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).<br></p>"
